163
00:15:53,140 --> 00:15:58,690
-ness, -ness, -ness. Business. Monkey business.

164
00:15:58,690 --> 00:16:03,400
Monkey suit. That’s what I’m wearing!
That’s the literal meaning. But there’s

165
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:09,540
