172
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:52,010
words ‘on’, and the next function word,
whether it’s ‘my’, ‘your’, ‘his’,

173
00:16:52,010 --> 00:16:57,830
or ‘her’, will be unstressed. So, ‘on
my’, ‘on my’, those two words will be

174
00:16:57,830 --> 00:17:04,470
